Name: Lokir Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Lesser Lokir Rune, Level 2 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes trickery and cunning, allowing those who channel it the ability to manipulate the conniving darkness.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACETapestry of FalsehoodSPACEAs an action, you attempt to twist the mind of a creature that you can see within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or see their allies as foes for TIME2-4TIME rounds.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 3 runic attunement slots. Requires Charisma 15 or greater to attune.
